Titolo: 911 Operator (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: 911 Operator is a 2017 simulation video game developed by Polish studio Jutsu Games and published by PlayWay. In the game, the player assumes the role of a 9-1-1 telephone operator who must answer phone calls and dispatch police officers, paramedics, and firefighters to various emergencies. 9•1•1 Operator was funded through a successful Kickstarter campaign that ran from July 21 to August 20, 2016. The game was released on PC in February 2017, with releases for the PlayStation 4 and Xbox One following later that year. The Android version of the game was released on November 16, 2017. On October 26, 2018, the game was released for Nintendo Switch. A sequel, 112 Operator, was released on April 23, 2020 on PC via Steam. It is also released on October 22, 2020 on Google Play for Android mobile.

Genere: Simulation 

Valutazione: N/A
